# "Fell in love with coser 5" is a live-action video interactive game.
<!--text-->
"Fell in love with coser 5" is a live-action video interactive game.
The game takes you into the world of the main character, where you have complex interactions with 9beautiful women, and the game does not contain romantic elements and a touching plot.

This game is the 9th live-action video interactive game filmed and produced by Thermae Studio, the story follows the previous game, and the players have finally started the competition prepared in the previous game, and the girls change into cosplay costumes and start to interact with you closely.
Thank you again for the support and encouragement of the players and teachers, the game theme is very niche, destined not to be liked by most players, if you are eager to experience love or rich plot, it is obvious that you have chosen the wrong game, the producer of the game does not believe in love, and there is no sufficient funds, and the touching love story of friends and businessmen cannot be made, the total production cost is less than 60,000 yuan, it should be the lowest production cost in similar games, the worst plot of the game! (disagreeing), the reason why it can continue to be produced depends on the players, thank you again to all the parents who support the purchase of the game, I will try to make progress slowly (not in the plot and cost), I will try to choose more generous, beautiful and generous beautiful actresses for everyone, let us skip love and go to the point!
The producers still use steel on the blade, and if you're a fan of blades, then I promise you'll collect all of my games without exception!

I hope this time will not disappoint the old players, and I hope to open a window for new players!
If you are looking for pure love, please do not play this game, because the game will not only ruin your purity, but also make you lose interest in pure love!
